name: viseto
tag_list: home-page-translations, homepage-translation-services, homepage-translator, website-translator, website-transations, site-translation, translation-websites
overview:
viseto offers inexpensive and professional translation of your website while retaining your current site design. The company provide translation and technology from one source. assistance of the customer’s system administrator or web designer is not required.

viseto generates an identical clone of the website in a different language. The structure and appearance of the translated version is adopted from the customer’s current web site. Access to server/s or Content Management System is not necessary.

The translated version of the internet site is then accessible under a new domain and will by hosted by viseto.

Changes to the original site are automatically transferred to the translated version. Thus all translated web pages are permanently kept up-to-date without incurring further time or effort for the customer!
